categories: Category:The Star Wars Holiday Special actors

nodes.text: Art Carney (November 4, 1918 - November 9, 2003) portrayed Saun Dann in The Star Wars Holiday Special. He is best known for his portrayal of Ed Norton in the classic television sitcom The Honeymooners. He died in November 9, 2003, five days after his 85th birthday and eight days before the 25th anniversary of the Holiday Special.
